Privacy Policy for Christian Miamor Dating App

Effective Date: 02/09/2025

Christian Miamor Dating App (“we,” “our,” or “us”) respects and values your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your information when you use our app. By using our service, you consent to this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect

Account Information: Email address, username, date of birth (to ensure age eligibility: 18+ only), gender, and optional profile details (photos, bio, preferences).

Usage Data: Information about your interactions within the app (likes, contact requests, acceptances, declines).

Device Information: Device model, operating system, unique identifiers, and approximate location (for matching purposes).

How We Use Your Information

To create and manage your account.

To match you with potential connections.

To send contact request notifications.

To improve our app and user experience.

To display personalized advertisements (our main revenue source).

Sharing of Information

With Other Users: Only information you choose to share (such as your profile and approved contact details).

With Third-Party Advertisers: Aggregated and anonymized data may be used for ad targeting.

As Required by Law: If legally mandated to comply with authorities.

Data Security

We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to safeguard your data against unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.

Data Retention

Your information will be retained as long as you have an active account or as needed to provide our services. You can request deletion of your data at any time.

Your Rights

You may access, update, or delete your personal information through the app settings or by contacting us at weezardinc@gmail.com

Children’s Privacy

Our service is strictly for users aged 18 years and above. We do not knowingly collect or process data from anyone under 18.

Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted in-app and updated here with a revised date.

Contact Us:
If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: weezardinc@gmail.com.
